---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import SectionHeading from "@/components/SectionHeading.astro";
import LeaderboardDemo from "@/components/LeaderboardDemo.astro";
---
<Layout
  title="Leaderboards · Tournamental"
  description="Global, country, and friend-group leaderboards across every tournament. Climb. Share. Earn badges. Bonus tokens for referrals."
  ogImage="/og/leaderboards.png"
>
  <section class="container-page pt-16 pb-12">
    <SectionHeading
      eyebrow="Leaderboards"
      title="Three scopes. Three timeframes. One game."
      lede="The whole world is on the global board. Your country is on the country board. Your office, your group chat, your fan club is on its own. They all update in real time as matches settle."
    />
    <div class="mt-10 max-w-2xl">
      <LeaderboardDemo />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container-page pb-12">
    <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-ink-700">
      <table class="w-full text-sm">
        <thead class="bg-ink-800 text-ink-200">
          <tr>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold">Scope</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold">All-time</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold">Season</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold">Weekly</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody class="text-ink-200">
          <tr class="border-t border-ink-700">
            <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium text-white">Global</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3">✓ Top 10,000</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3">✓ Top 10,000</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3">✓ Top 1,000</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-t border-ink-700">
            <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium text-white">Country</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3">✓ Top 1,000</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3">✓ Top 1,000</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3">✓ Top 250</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-t border-ink-700">
            <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium text-white">Tournament</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3">-</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3">-</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3">✓ All</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-t border-ink-700">
            <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium text-white">Syndicate (private)</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3">✓ All</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3">✓ All</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3">✓ All</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container-page pb-12">
    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-6">How you score</h3>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="card">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-white">Points per call</h4>
        <p class="text-ink-200 mt-2">Base points for a correct prediction, scaled by how unlikely the call was at lock-in. Calling a 50/50 nets you base; calling a 7-1 longshot nets you ~7x.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-white">Streak multipliers</h4>
        <p class="text-ink-200 mt-2">Daily prediction streak compounds. Match-day streak compounds harder during a tournament. Hot-hand bonus on consecutive correct calls.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-white">Prediction IQ</h4>
        <p class="text-ink-200 mt-2">Rolling Brier-score that travels with you. Top IQs get featured on the global landing, and yes, it's hard to game (we score against the closing line).</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-white">Badges + bonus tokens</h4>
        <p class="text-ink-200 mt-2">Bronze through Mythic. Some are skill-based, some are showing-up based, some are sharing based. Tokens convert to extra entries and cosmetics, never to cash.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container-prose pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Anti-bot, pro-fan</h2>
    <p class="prose-vt">A Humanness Score (per the open-source spec) prevents bot accounts from gaming the boards. If we suspect inauthentic behaviour, payouts and badge unlocks clamp until verification. The score is computed from cross-provider OAuth (Telegram, Discord, Apple, Google) plus optional contacts-cluster verification, we never sell who you know.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-10">No pay-to-win</h2>
    <p class="prose-vt">There's no way to buy points. There's no way to buy a leaderboard slot. Bonus tokens come from playing, sharing, and referring. The whole spec is on <a href="/open-source" class="link">GitHub</a>, audit it yourself.</p>
  </section>
</Layout>
